dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Lonoak quadrangle, Monterey and San Benito counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Lonoak CA 1969. Photorevised 1984. DMA 1856 IV SW, series V895." "First printing, April 2007." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1970. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1972.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
